text: Robin Williams is a British slalom canoeist who competed in the 1980s. He won two medals in the C-2 team event at the ICF Canoe Slalom World Championships with a gold in 1981 and a bronze in 1983. ==References== Category:British sportspeople Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Canoeists
